      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By December 15, 1945.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Indiantown Gap, Pennsylvania.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, whenever we arrived in the States, they had a big dinner prepared for us at-- at Indiantown Gap, a steak dinner.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Potatoes and vegetables and so forth.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was something that my body was crying for.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't no meat and potatoes.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Milk.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this mess sergeant told me that most of the soldiers coming back was craving this milk, fresh milk, because we had to use powdered milk the whole time we were over there.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "mixed",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I took a number 56 dipper, which is about a quart, and I stood there.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a big 20-gallon pot with a spigot on it, merged in ice to keep it nice and cold.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I take this number 56 dipper, which is about a quart, and I drank about four of those.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reliving",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had-- was no room for no steak and potatoes.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] I just wanted milk.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "mixed",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I got home, my mother was getting two quarts of milk a day for the family.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "resolution",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I told her, put two more.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll pay for it.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Get two more quarts.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_narration",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she ordered two more quarts.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then as I settled down, I would get in the mornings when I'd get up, I'd eat a half a pound of bacon, about six eggs, and drink a quart of milk for breakfast [INAUDIBLE] before I had eggs and bacon, mostly.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "habitual_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then cereals, oatmeal, and all that sort of thing.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "habitual_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got home in '45.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Three years later I got married.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got married in '48.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "October 6, 1948.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I have three children, three boys.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my oldest son--",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "William Paul, Jr.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He has a degree in architecture.",
      "memory_type": "external",
