      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "resolution",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had his degree in business administration.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a tax accountant.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He worked for Internal Revenue downtown.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He worked for the city in their tax division.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, when he was working for Internal Revenue, they-- most of the other personnel working there, they would load his desk up with all this work, paperwork, whilst they goofed off at the water fountain and the coffee machine.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "habitual_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I told him, no, you don't need that.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I made him give it up, because anytime you have a disability, you automatically get $150 Social Security.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I didn't think that was adequate for a young man, so I put him on my Social Security.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so they took so much out of my Social Security and added to it and made him get about $300 of mine.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd be delighted to meet them.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd be-- I'd be delighted to meet them.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you know, I would say how wonderful, fine young men you've grown up to be and so forth.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just be overwhelmed to see that they had prospered.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then--",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I have no idea.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would probably say thank you for feeding us [DRINKS] when we were hungry.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I doubt very seriously.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know where they are today.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why is it important?",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it's important to let the generation come-- coming along know that life is not all peaches and cream.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some-- and to be a true red-blooded American, sometime you have to make certain sacrifices.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And making sacrifices is not fighting among each other and getting involved with the wrong people.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never dreamed that I'd seen drugs and so forth destroying our communities and so forth.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never dreamed that I'd see gangsters and racketeers taking over, getting the upper hand in our communities and so forth.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even today, I-- I never thought that I would see the day come where every time you turn the television on, it's full with nothing but violence.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what's the society coming to?",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is there anything else you would like to say that we may not have-- that you may not have spoken about before during your testimony?",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "other",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "other",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was not liberated.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "liberation",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I had completed my tour of duty in the military, well, after the war in Europe, I was in the Army Reserve.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And came out of the Army Reserve and went back and served an additional year, assisting the wounded soldiers at Howard General Hospital on Staten Island returning home.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that's where I made sergeant.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was discharged with the rank of PFC.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At Howard General Hospital, where I was promoted to sergeant, then I was-- then I came out, got discharged from-- I was getting ready to make a career out of the Army.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "mixed",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got discharged because of family concerns.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to work.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was up to be promoted to master sergeant and shipped back over to Germany because of my previous experience in Germany.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I turned it down.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I was discharged a second time, I turned it down, come home to assist with securing my family.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "post-war",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's time to lend every effort of one's being in trying to establish peace and harmony throughout communities, throughout these United States of America, and throughout the world without bloodshed.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's time that we come to our senses and eliminate bloodshed.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because war is hell.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "War is horrible.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
